{
  "description": "A breathtaking long-distance shot of a seascape dominated by dramatic light rays piercing through dark, billowing clouds. The sun, though not directly visible, casts a golden glow that illuminates the water and highlights the landscape. In the distance, a suspension bridge stretches across the water, connecting hills or mountains on either side. A darker landmass is visible near the bottom of the frame, appearing as a silhouette against the brighter water. Several small boats are dotted across the water, adding scale and detail to the scene. The overall composition evokes a sense of vastness and serenity, with a touch of dramatic intensity from the cloud formations and light effects.",
